:: Gwylan Hypnosis Start
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set _hideHypnosisOptions to true>>

<<if $gwylan.requestLast?.hold is $phase>>
	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>
			"C-can we continue now, please?" you ask.
		<<case "bratty">>
			"Alright, I did what you wanted, can we continue now?" you ask.
		<<default>>
			"May we continue where we left off now?" you ask.
	<</switch>>
<<else>>
	<<switch $phase>>
		<<case "peace">>
			<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("hypnosis_peace")>>
				<<switch $speech_attitude>>
					<<case "meek">>"Y-you said you could help me with this," you say, gesturing to your unusual parts.
					<<case "bratty">>"So, can you help me with all this?" you ask, gesturing to your unusual parts.
					<<default>>"You said you could help me with my inner self," you say, gesturing to your unusual parts.
				<</switch>>
			<<else>>
				<<switch $speech_attitude>>
					<<case "meek">>"C-can you help me with my inner self again?" you ask.
					<<case "bratty">>"I need your help keeping my inner self under control again," you say.
					<<default>>"Could you help me come to terms with my inner self again?" you ask.
				<</switch>>
			<</if>>
		<<case "silence">>
			<<switch $speech_attitude>>
				<<case "meek">>"C-can you make <<if numberOfEarSlime() gt 1>>these things in my ears<<else>>this thing in my ear<</if>> stop?" you ask.
				<<case "bratty">>"Please, for the love of god, shut <<if numberOfEarSlime() gt 1>>these things in my ears<<else>>this thing in my ear<</if>> up," you say.
				<<default>>"Could you help me with <<if numberOfEarSlime() gt 1>>these things in my ears<<else>>this thing in my ear<</if>>?" you ask.
			<</switch>>
		<<case "slumber">>
			<<switch $speech_attitude>>
				<<case "meek">>"I-I've been having trouble sleeping," you say. "Can you help?"
				<<case "bratty">>"I need my beauty sleep, but it's not coming easy," you say. "Can you help?"
				<<default>>"I've been having trouble sleeping. Can you help?" you ask.
			<</switch>>
		<<case "insight">>
			<<switch $speech_attitude>>
				<<case "meek">>"I-I've been seeing things," you say. "Can you help?"
				<<case "bratty">>"I think I'm losing it. I'm seeing things that can't be real," you say. "Can you help?"
				<<default>>"I've been seeing things. Can you help?" you ask.
			<</switch>>
		<<case "removal">>
			<<switch $speech_attitude>>
				<<case "meek">>"I-I think someone else is in my head," you say. "Can you make it stop?"
				<<case "bratty">>"Someone's got my brain in a twist, I think. Can you help?" you ask.
				<<default>>"I don't feel like myself. I have strange impulses, and I think someone else hypnotised me," you explain.
			<</switch>>
		<<default>>
			<<set _hypnosisError to true>>
	<</switch>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if _hypnosisError>>
	You open your naughty mouth to ask Gwylan for help, but the only thing that comes out is salt. A branch slaps you square on the ass for your troubles. <<pain 2>><<arousal 200>><<gpain>><<garousal>>
	<br><br>

	"What?" Gwylan says. "Could you repeat that please?"
	<br><br>

	<span class="red">This is a bug. Please report this. phase: <<print $phase>></span>
	<br><br>

	<<set $phase to 0>>
	<<gwylanOptions>>
<<elseif !$settings.hypnosisEnabled>>
	Gwylan smiles sadly. "<span class="blue">You've closed up your mind.</span> There's nothing I can do for you until you open it to being changed through <span class="purple">hypnosis</span>."
	<br><br>

	<i><span class="blue">Hypnosis must be enabled to continue.</span></i>
	<br><br>

	<<set $phase to 0>>
	<<gwylanOptions>>
<<elseif $daily.gwylan.hypnosis and !$gwylanSeen.includes("yearning")>>
	Gwylan holds up <<his>> hands towards you. "One per day is enough for now. You need to pace yourself. Give it time to stick."
	<br><br>

	<<set $phase to 0>>
	<<gwylanOptions>>
<<elseif $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte gwylanHypnoMax("trait") and !$gwylanSeen.includes("hypnosis_deepest") and $hypnosisTimers?.devotion.time + 10 > gwylanHypnoMax("value")>>
	<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 4 and !$gwylanSeen.includes("hypnosis_deepest")>>
		Gwylan frowns, but blushes. "You know the side effects deepen each time. You're already..."
		<br><br>

		<<He>> raises <<his>> hand, and a single finger. Your eyes lock on it. <<He>> then cups <<his>> hand near your face. <<hypnosisText "You raise your head instinctively, and <<he>> scratches under your chin.">>
		<br><br>

		"...trapped in my web," <<he>> says with a guilty laugh. "I'm afraid I'll break you if I let this go any further."
		<<if _gwylanLovePercent gte 80 and _gwylanStatus.includes("lust") and !$weekly.gwylanDeepest>>
			<<His>> thumb rubs your cheek. "Yet, a part of me wants this. To just give in and..."
			<br><br>

			<<His>> face comes close to yours. You feel <<his>> breath on your lips, but <<he>> stops short of kissing you. After a moment's hesitation, <<he>> releases you and steps around you.
			You turn to follow <<him>>. "<span class="witch">Stay,</span>" <<he>> says. <<hypnosisText "Your body obeys without question.">>
			<br><br>

			You feel <<his>> chin rest on your shoulder.
			"If you truly want this..." <<His>> whisper slides into your ears and echoes. Visions of your acts with Gwylan swim in schools, displacing the currents of your mental ocean.
			<<His>> breath tickles your ear. "Prove it." A thin red powder is drawn under your nose, and the visions dry up. <<llarousal>><<arousal -2000>>
			<br><br>

			"This will only last a minute." <<He>> steps back in front of you. "Sit."
			<br><br>

			<span class="teal">The usual compulsion isn't present.</span> <<He>> smiles. "If we sink any further, <span class="red">you won't be able to say 'no' to me until the hypnosis wears off.</span> So I need to hear the words from your mouth. I need to make sure it's <i>you</i> that wants this."
			<br><br>

			<<link [[Do nothing|Gwylan Hypnosis Deepest]]>><<set $phase2 to 1>><<npcincr Gwylan dom -5>><</link>><<llyearning>>
			<br>
			<<link [[Sit and tell <<him>> you want this|Gwylan Hypnosis Deepest]]>><<set $phase2 to 2>><<sub 1>><</link>>
			<br>
		<<else>>
			<<He>> lowers <<his>> hand, leaving you feeling cold. "You were never meant to fall this deep in. I'm sorry. Let it fade for a while, please. For both of our sakes.
			You should be ready again
			<<set _canRefreshHypnosisIn to $hypnosisTimers.devotion.time - (gwylanHypnoMax("value") - 10)>>
			<<if _canRefreshHypnosisIn is 1>>
				<span class="gold">tomorrow</span>."
			<<else>>
				in <span class="gold"><<number _canRefreshHypnosisIn>> days</span>."
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			<<if $weekly.gwylanDeepest>>
				<span class="blue"><<He>> believes your requests are not your own, and that you have sunken too deep. Given time, <<he>> may be open to the possibility again.</span>
			<<else>>
				<span class="blue">There was hesitation in <<his>> voice. If pushed further into <span class="forest-green">yearning</span>, <<he>> might not show restraint.</span>
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			<<set $phase to 0>>
			<<gwylanOptions>>
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("ritual_beast")>>
			<<if $phase is "silence">>
				Gwylan frowns. "I'm sorry, <span class="blue">but you're not ready to go any deeper into my trance yet</span>. I'm... I'm afraid of what you'd do for me, were I to ask. You'll have to hang in there for a little while longer."
			<<else>>
				Gwylan giggles. "I appreciate your enthusiasm, <span class="blue">but you're not ready to go deeper into my trance yet</span>. For both of our sakes, we shouldn't allow our... attachment... to go that far. You may end up doing something you regret if we do. Give your mind time to rationalise and recover."
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			Gwylan shakes <<his>> head. "<span class="blue">You aren't ready to slip deeper into my trance.</span> Not yet, at least. The side effects are only harmless so long as we give you time to recover."
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		<<He>> steps aside, and motions for you to follow. <<He>> pulls out a chair and has you sit.
		<br><br>

		"Just hold still a moment, dear." <<He>> leans in to look into your eyes. <<He>> then raises <<his>> hand, and snaps <<his>> fingers in various directions to measure your responsiveness.
		<<He>> asks you several questions pertaining to how you feel about <<him>>, interspersed with seemingly random ones such as what you had for breakfast.
		<br><br>

		<<He>> places a hand to <<his>> chin in thought. "You should be ready again...
		<<set _canRefreshHypnosisIn to $hypnosisTimers.devotion.time - (gwylanHypnoMax("value") - 10)>>
		<<if _canRefreshHypnosisIn is 1>>
			<span class="gold">tomorrow</span>."
		<<else>>
			in <span class="gold"><<number _canRefreshHypnosisIn>> days</span>."
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		<<set $phase to 0>>
		<<gwylanOptions>>
	<</if>>
<<elseif $phase isnot "removal" and $hypnosisTimers[$phase] and $hypnosisTimers[$phase]?.time gt Math.floor($hypnosisTimers[$phase]?.max / 2) and !$gwylanSeen.includes("hypnosis_deepest")>>
	Gwylan tilts <<his>> head. "The effects from last time should still be holding strong. Just hold still a moment, dear." <<He>> leans in to look into your eyes. <<He>> then raises <<his>> hand, and snaps <<his>> fingers in various directions to measure your responsiveness.
	<br><br>

	<<He>> places a hand to <<his>> chin in thought. "If you don't wish to leave any gaps in the effects, we should be able to perform that technique again...
	<<set _canRefreshHypnosisIn to $hypnosisTimers[$phase].time - Math.floor($hypnosisTimers[$phase]?.max / 2)>>
	<<if _canRefreshHypnosisIn is 1>>
		<span class="gold">tomorrow</span>."
	<<else>>
		in <span class="gold"><<number _canRefreshHypnosisIn>> days</span>."
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<set $phase to 0>>
	<<gwylanOptions>>
<<elseif !$gwylan.requestDone>>
	<<if $gwylan.request.event>>
		Gwylan thinks for a moment. "Sure, but only after <span class="blue">you do what I asked of you</span>."
	<<else>>
		<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("request_intro")>>
			Gwylan thinks for a moment. "I can help, but I need you to do something for me first. It'll be nice and simple, don't worry." <<He>> smiles sweetly.
			<<run gwylanRequest("tutorial")>>
			<<gwylanRequestText>>
		<<else>>
			Gwylan thinks for a moment. "I can help, but I need you to do something for me first." <<He>> smiles sweetly.
			<<run gwylanRequest()>>
			<<gwylanRequestText>>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
	<<set $gwylan.request.hold to $phase>>
	<br><br>

	<<set $phase to 0>>
	<<gwylanOptions>>
<<else>>
	<<if $phase is "removal" and !$gwylanSeen.includes("hypnosis_removal")>>
		Gwylan nods. "I should warn you that there will be temporary side effects. Simply removing the impulses isn't possible, that would require erasing entire memories.
		Instead, I'll be <span class="pink">replacing them</span> with something that will fade naturally over time. <span class="red">There's a risk of damage to your psyche.</span> If you're alright with that, we can continue whenever you're ready."
	<<elseif !$gwylanSeen.includes("hypnosis_intro")>>
		Gwylan nods. "You'll need to trust me for it to work. It won't last long, but we can always redo it at a later date. There's also a limit to how much your mind can take at once.
		<<if $phase is "slumber">>
			<span class="blue">This particular method will require you to fall asleep, and may take up to a few hours.</span>
		<</if>>
		<span class="blue">There will be temporary side effects,</span> too. We can start whenever you're ready."
	<<elseif $phase is "slumber" and !$gwylanSeen.includes("hypnosis_slumber")>>
		Gwylan smiles. "<span class="blue">This particular method will require you to fall asleep, and may take up to a few hours.</span> We can start whenever you're ready."
	<<elseif _gwylanStatus.includes("lust") && $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 5>>
		Gwylan smiles. "You want to go yet deeper, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "my">>?" <<He>> cups under your chin. "Strange. I can't seem to say no to you. You must know what that's like by now."
	<<else>>
		Gwylan smiles. "Of course. We can start whenever you're ready. As you know, there will be temporary side effects."
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<switch $phase>>
		<<case "peace">><<hypnosisicon>><<link [[Let Gwylan hypnotise you (1:00)|Gwylan Hypnosis Start 2]]>><<pass 10>><<endevent>><<set $phase to "peace">><</link>><<gwylanHypnoNote>>
		<<case "silence">><<hypnosisicon>><<link [[Let Gwylan hypnotise you (1:00)|Gwylan Hypnosis Start 2]]>><<pass 10>><<endevent>><<set $phase to "silence">><</link>><<gwylanHypnoNote>>
		<<case "slumber">><<hypnosisicon>><<link [[Let Gwylan hypnotise you (1:00)|Gwylan Hypnosis Start 2]]>><<pass 10>><<endevent>><<set $phase to "slumber">><</link>><<gwylanHypnoNote>>
		<<case "insight">><<hypnosisicon>><<link [[Let Gwylan hypnotise you (1:00)|Gwylan Hypnosis Start 2]]>><<pass 10>><<endevent>><<set $phase to "insight">><</link>><<gwylanHypnoNote>>
		<<case "removal">><<hypnosisicon>><<link [[Let Gwylan hypnotise you (1:00)|Gwylan Hypnosis Start 2]]>><<pass 10>><<endevent>><<set $phase to "removal">><</link>><<gwylanHypnoNote>>
	<</switch>>
	<br><br>

	<<set $phase to 0>>
	<<gwylanOptions>>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Start 2
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $outside to 0>><<set $location to "forest_shop_garden">>
<<npc Gwylan>><<person1>>
<<set $gwylan.requestDone to false>>
<<if $gwylan.requestLast?.hold>>
	<<run delete $gwylan.requestLast.hold>>
<</if>>
<<set $hypnosis_potency to Math.ceil($hypnosis_traits.devotion / 2) || 1>>

<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("garden_seen")>>
	<<if C.npc.Gwylan.dom gte 20>>
		<<He>> takes your hand and leads you to the garden. <<takeHandholdingVirginity "Gwylan" "consensual">>
	<<else>>
		<<He>> leads you to the garden.
	<</if>>
	You sit down on the large cushion in the covered room.
	<br><br>
<<else>>
	<<He>> places a black blindfold over your eyes. "Sorry, but my garden is usually off-limits. I can't have anyone knowing how to get in."
	<br><br>

	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("garden")>>
		<<He>> steadily walks you to the garden before removing it. <<He>> sits you down on a large cushion in the covered room.
	<<else>>
		<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("garden")>>
		<<He>> steadily walks you somewhere. You hear doors open and shut. Eventually, you smell roses and feel the fresh air on your skin. <<He>> removes your blindfold.
		A large expanse of square stone tiles stretch along the ground, connecting patches of grass and raised sections filled with dirt, flowers and herbs.
		Surrounding it all is an impressive weaving of crossed wooden stakes well over two metres high, with gaps just large enough to allow vines to grab and climb through, shielding the whole area from prying outside eyes.
		<br><br>

		There's another raised section, but this one is different. It's covered by a wooden roof,
		<<if Weather.precipitation is "rain" or Weather.precipitation is "snow">>
			untouched by the <<print Weather.precipitation>>,
		<</if>>
		and the inside is padded with various cushions and quilts. Gwylan leads you over to it, sitting you down on a large cushion.
		<br><br>
	<</if>>
<</if>>

Gwylan leaves momentarily, returning with a tray that holds a teacup, many herbs, and a mortar and pestle. <<He>> places it in front of you on a small table.
<<if $worn.handheld.name isnot "naked">>
	You set your <<= $worn.handheld.name>> aside.
	<<handheldundress "gwylanHypno">>
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<He>> walks around the garden, picking a few herbs and tossing them into the mortar and pestle. <<He>> hums as <<he>> grinds them together.
<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("hypnosis_intro")>>
	When <<hes>> done, <<he>> gently grabs your arm and runs <<his>> fingernails down it, just enough to leave some small marks. You instinctively pull your arm away. "What are you doing?"
	<br><br>

	<<He>> gently grabs your arm again. "Simple allergy test." <<He>> rubs the freshly ground herbs on the marks <<he>> left, and watches closely. Nothing happens for several minutes. "Excellent."
	<<He>> adds the herbs to a filter.
<<else>>
	<<He>> finishes grinding up the herbs, and adds them to a filter.
<</if>>
<<He>> then pours the hot water from the teapot through it, into the cup. "Drink this first. It's a herbal tea that will help you relax."
<br><br>

<<He>> turns away and lights a hanging incense burner. <<hallucinogen 20>>
<br><br>

<<link [[Drink the tea|Gwylan Hypnosis Start 3]]>><<pass 10>><<set $phase2 to "drink">><<stress -14>><<tiredness 3>><<hallucinogen 200>><<set $hypnosis_potency++>><</link>><<llstress>><<gtiredness>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>>
<br>
<<link [[Don't drink it|Gwylan Hypnosis Start 3]]>><<pass 10>><<set $phase2 to "no">><</link>><<gwylanWillpowerDifficulty>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Start 3
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>

<<if $phase2 is "no">>
	You decide against drinking it. Gwylan sits down at the opposite side of the small table, on a cushion of <<his>> own.
	<<if !$willpowerSuccess>>
		<<He>> frowns upon seeing the cup still full. "It won't bite, dear." <<He>> scoots over to your side of the table. "Here, just relax." <<He>> puts a hand on your shoulder.
		<br><br>

		<<hypnosisText "Your body won't move, yearning to be guided by <<him>>. <span class='red'><<He>> knows what's best.</span>">>
		<br><br>

		<<He>> lifts the cup to your lips, and you drink obediently. "There. See?" <<He>> strokes your head for a moment. You don't know what you were worried about.
		You relish in <span class="witch"><<his>></span> warmth. You find your arms and eyelids feeling heavier already.
		<<stress -12>><<tiredness 3>><<hallucinogen 200>><<set $hypnosis_potency++>><<llstress>><<gtiredness>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>>
	<<else>>
		<<He>> frowns upon seeing the cup still full, but doesn't mention it.
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	<<wearProp "tea">>
	You sip the tea, relishing in its warmth. You find your arms and eyelids feeling heavier already. Gwylan sits down at the opposite side of the small table, on a cushion of <<his>> own.
<</if>>
<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("hypnosis_intro")>>
<br><br>

<<switch $phase>>
	<<case "peace">>
		"Tell me, dear. What is it about your inner self that bothers you?"
		<br><br>

		<<if $fox gte 4 and $gwylanSeen.includes("romance")>>
			<<His>> gaze lingers on you for a moment too long.
			<br><br>
		<</if>>

		<<link [[It attracts too much attention|Gwylan Hypnosis Peace]]>><<set $phase to "attention">><<stress 18>><</link>><<ggstress>>
		<br>
		<<link [[It's not who I am|Gwylan Hypnosis Peace]]>><<set $phase to "identity">><<trauma 18>><</link>><<ggtrauma>>
		<br>
		<<if $cow gte 4>>
			<<link [[Painful memories of the farm|Gwylan Hypnosis Peace]]>><<set $phase to "cow">><<trauma -3>><</link>><<ltrauma>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
		<<if $fallenangel gte 2 or $demon gte 6>>
			<<link [[Regret and shame for lost purity|Gwylan Hypnosis Peace]]>><<set $phase to "purity">><<stress 14>><<trauma -6>><</link>><<ggstress>><<ltrauma>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
		<<if ($wolfgirl gte 2 or $cat gte 2 or $cow gte 2 or $fox gte 2) and (playerHeatMinArousal() + playerRutMinArousal()) gte 1>>
			<<if playerHeatMinArousal() gte 1 and playerRutMinArousal() gte 1>>
				<<link [[Bothered by heat and rut|Gwylan Hypnosis Peace]]>><<set $phase to "heat">><<npcincr Gwylan lust 2>><</link>><<glust>>
			<<elseif playerRutMinArousal() gte 1>>
				<<link [[Bothered by rut|Gwylan Hypnosis Peace]]>><<set $phase to "heat">><<npcincr Gwylan lust 2>><</link>><<glust>>
			<<else>>
				<<link [[Bothered by heat|Gwylan Hypnosis Peace]]>><<set $phase to "heat">><<npcincr Gwylan lust 2>><</link>><<glust>>
			<</if>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
	<<case "silence">>
		<<He>> moves behind you and places <<his>> fingers under your ears. "Relax." <<His>> touch makes you shiver. <<He>> rubs the area for a moment, as if feeling for something.
		<br><br>

		"This may feel strange." <<He>> tilts your head to the side, and you feel a temperate liquid enter your ear canal.
		<<if numberOfEarSlime(true) gte 2>>
			<<He>> then tilts your head the other way and repeats with your other ear.
		<</if>>
		"It will keep <<if numberOfEarSlime(true) gte 2>>them<<else>>it<</if>> quiet until I can work."
		<br><br>

		<<link [[Next|Gwylan Hypnosis Silence]]>><</link>>
		<br>
	<<case "slumber">>
		"Tell me, why do you think sleep evades you?"
		<br><br>

		<<if $dissociation gte 1 and $controlled is 0>>
			<<link [[Say you can't tell what's real|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber]]>><<set $phase to "dissociation">><</link>>
			<br>
		<<else>>
			<<link [[Say you just have trouble falling asleep|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber]]>><<set $phase to "insomnia">><</link>>
			<br>
			<<if $nightmares gte 1>>
				<<link [[Say you have nightmares|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber]]>><<set $phase to "nightmares">><</link>>
				<br>
			<</if>>
			<<if $anxiety gte 1>>
				<<link [[Say you're often too anxious to get restful sleep|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber]]>><<set $phase to "anxiety">><</link>>
				<br>
			<</if>>
			<<if $panicattacks gte 1>>
				<<link [[Say you have panic attacks in your sleep|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber]]>><<set $phase to "panic">><</link>>
				<br>
			<</if>>
			<<if $flashbacks gte 1>>
				<<link [[Say you have recurring nightmares of the torment you've faced|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber]]>><<set $phase to "flashbacks">><</link>>
				<br>
			<</if>>
			<<if $dissociation gte 1>>
				<<link [[Say you can't tell what's real|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber]]>><<set $phase to "dissociation">><</link>>
				<br>
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
	<<case "insight">>
		"What is it you see, that you should not?"
		<br><br>

		<<if $settings.tentaclesEnabled>>
			<<link [[Unnatural monsters with many limbs|Gwylan Hypnosis Insight]]>><<set $phase to "tentacles">><</link>>
			<br>
			<<if $settings.plantsEnabled>>
				<<link [[Plants that attack with branches, roots and vines|Gwylan Hypnosis Insight]]>><<set $phase to "plants">><</link>>
				<br>
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
		<<if $settings.slimesEnabled>>
			<<link [[Slime that moves with a will of its own|Gwylan Hypnosis Insight]]>><<set $phase to "slimes">><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
		<<if $settings.monsterHallucinationsOnly and $settings.monsterChance gte 1>>
			<<link [[Animals with human characteristics|Gwylan Hypnosis Insight]]>><<set $phase to "monsters">><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
		<<if $temple_confessor_intro>>
			<<link [[Holes in the world itself|Gwylan Hypnosis Insight]]>><<set $phase to "holes">><</link>>
			<br>
		<<else>>
			<<link [[Lots of little things that should not be|Gwylan Hypnosis Insight]]>><<set $phase to "lots">><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
	<<case "removal">>
		"Tell me about these impulses, as well as any gaps in your memory."
		<br><br>

		<<if $hypnosis_traits.suggestion gte 1>>
			<<link [[Tell <<him>> about Harper's treatments|Gwylan Hypnosis Removal]]>><<set $phase to "suggestion">><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
		<<if $hypnosis_traits.scream gte 1>>
			<<link [[Tell <<him>> about your inability to scream for help|Gwylan Hypnosis Removal]]>><<set $phase to "scream">><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
		<<if $hypnosis_traits.cover gte 1>>
			<<link [[Tell <<him>> about your urge to flaunt|Gwylan Hypnosis Removal]]>><<set $phase to "cover">><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
		<<if $hypnosis_traits.deviancy gte 1>>
			<<link [[Tell <<him>> about your urge to provoke beasts|Gwylan Hypnosis Removal]]>><<set $phase to "deviancy">><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
		<<link [[Tell <<him>> that you can't remember|Gwylan Hypnosis Removal]]>><<set $phase to "forgot">><</link>>
		<br>
	<<default>>
		You blink, and realise that none of this actually happened.
		<<if !($phase is "no" and $willpowerSuccess)>>That must have been some fucked up tea. Wait, did you even drink it?<</if>>
		You're still standing in the forest shop. <span class="red">This is a bug, please report.</span> <span class="blue">Hypnosis selection: <<print $phase>></span>
		<br><br>

		<<unset $hypnosis_potency>>
		<<endevent>><<npc Gwylan>><<person1>><<set $location to "forest_shop">>
		<<gwylanOptions>>
<</switch>>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Peace
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $phase is "attention">>
	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>"Everyone looks at me funny," you say. "More than usual."
		<<case "bratty">>"Too many people get the wrong idea," you say.
		<<default>>"I get too many looks," you say. "I got too many before all this, it's just worse now."
	<</switch>>
	<br><br>

	Gwylan thinks for a moment, picking more herbs.
	<<if _gwylanTF.known>>
		<<if $fox gte 6>>
			"It's hard, isn't it? Us foxes are the favoured victims. Always the first choice, the prize for a hunt."
		<<else>>
			"I can relate, but not for the same reasons."
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		"I understand. It's difficult enough without them."
	<</if>>
<<elseif $phase is "identity">>
	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>"I didn't want this," you say. "It just happened."
		<<case "bratty">>"I didn't ask for it," you say. "It just happened to me, but it's not me."
		<<default>>"I'm not comfortable with this," you say. "It's not me."
	<</switch>>
	<br><br>

	<<if $worn.neck.name is "familiar collar" and ($wolfgirl gte 4 or $cat gte 4 or $fox gte 4 or $cow gte 4 or $harpy gte 4)>>
		Gwylan caresses your familiar collar. "Your collar is preventing you from changing. It makes you wear your heart on your sleeve. Or neck, in this case."
		<<if $worn.neck.cursed is 1>>
			<<set _magicLeash to true>>
			Gwylan holds <<his>> hand up, and your leash appears.
			<<if $gwylan.taken>>
				"I can't allow you to remove it. I'll ensure you're at peace, and can hide away as you please. However, you should know that you can never truly hide yourself from me, my dear."
			<<else>>
				"If you wish to remove it, come speak to me. Until then, I'll ensure you're at peace."
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			<<set _selfFulfilling to true>>
		<</if>>
	<<elseif $wolfgirl gte 4 and $worn.neck.name.includes("spiked collar")>>
		<<set _selfFulfilling to true>>
		Gwylan walks up to you and
		<<if $worn.neck.type.includes("leash")>>
			holds your leash. "I think you make a cute puppy, for what it's worth." <<arousal 400>><<garousal>>
		<<else>>
			examines your spiked collar. "Well, this isn't helping if you want to be rid of it entirely. You're accepting it by wearing this."
		<</if>>
	<<elseif $cat gte 4 and $worn.neck.name is "cat bell collar">>
		<<set _selfFulfilling to true>>
		Gwylan walks up to you and examines your collar. "This little kitty bell certainly won't help your self-perception. You're accepting it by wearing this."
	<<elseif $fox gte 4 and ($worn.head.name is "spirit mask" or $worn.neck.name is "jasper pendant")>>
		<<set _selfFulfilling to true>>
		<<if $worn.head.name is "spirit mask" and $worn.neck.name is "jasper pendant">>
			Gwylan walks up and examines the spirit mask and jasper pendant you're wearing.
			<<if !$gwylanTalked.includesAny("shine", "jasper")>>
				"Firstly, these are wonderful, please come talk to me about where you got these later. Secondly, you're accepting it by wearing these."
			<<else>>
				"You have a strange way of showing dissatisfaction. You're accepting it by wearing these."
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			<<if $worn.head.name is "spirit mask">>
				Gwylan walks up and rubs <<his>> thumb over the mask on your head.
				<<if !$gwylanTalked.includes("shrine")>>
					"Firstly, this looks wonderful, please come talk to me about where you got it later. Secondly, you're accepting this manifestation by wearing it."
				<<else>>
					"You have a strange way of showing dissatisfaction. You're accepting it by wearing this."
				<</if>>
			<<else>>
				Gwylan walks up and rubs <<his>> thumb over the jasper pendant.
				<<if !$gwylanTalked.includes("jasper")>>
					"Firstly, this looks wonderful, please come talk to me about where you got it later. Secondly, you're accepting this manifestation by wearing it."
				<<else>>
					"You have a strange way of showing dissatisfaction. You're accepting it by wearing this."
				<</if>>
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
	<<elseif $cow gte 4 and $worn.neck.name is "cow bell">>
		<<set _selfFulfilling to true>>
		Gwylan walks up and pushes your cow bell with a finger, hearing it ring once. "You wear this willingly. If you wish to be rid of it, you'll need to shed this mark of submission and acceptance."
	<<elseif $harpy gte 4 and ($worn.head.name is "feathered hair clip" or $worn.neck.name is "feather necklace")>>
		<<set _selfFulfilling to true>>
		<<if $worn.head.name is "feathered hair clip" and $worn.neck.name is "feather necklace">>
			Gwylan walks up and examines the feathered accessories you're wearing.
			<<if !$gwylanTalked.includes("bird")>>
				"Firstly, these are wonderful, please come talk to me about where you got these later. Secondly, you're accepting it by wearing these."
			<<else>>
				"You're accepting it by wearing these, little birdie."
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			Gwylan walks up and examines the feather you're wearing.
			<<if !$gwylanTalked.includes("bird")>>
				"Firstly, this looks wonderful, please come talk to me about where you got it later. Secondly, you're accepting this manifestation by wearing it."
			<<else>>
				"You're accepting it by wearing this, little birdie."
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
	<<elseif $demon gte 6 and $worn.lower.name is "succubus lower back wings">>
		<<set _selfFulfilling to true>>
		Gwylan walks behind you and examines the fake wings on your lower back. "You seem to have accepted it, in a way. Is it true acceptance, or are you trying to fit a role you never asked to play?"
	<</if>>
	<<if _selfFulfilling>>
		<<He>> smiles, and <<his>> voice is gentle. "I understand it can be difficult to let go. There's a comfort in forcing your face to fit a mask. It's a dangerous game to play, though.
		Accepting something you don't want, making it part of your identity, can only help so much. When you finally begin to heal, you may feel as though you're losing a part of yourself."
		<br><br>
	<</if>>

	<<if $angel gte 4 and $transformationParts.angel.halo isnot "hidden">>
		<<His>> finger traces your halo. "There are ways to be rid of it, but losing this would break you. I can imagine the struggle," <<he>> says sadly.
	<<elseif $fallenangel gte 2 and $transformationParts.fallenAngel.wings isnot "hidden">>
		<<His>> fingers run up and down your broken wings.
		<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("fallen_fault")>>
			"Forgiveness doesn't... come easy." <<He>> can't make eye contact with you again. "I hope you can find it in your heart to forgive me some day."
		<<else>>
			"Forgiveness doesn't come easy, does it?" <<He>> smiles sadly. "Forgiving yourself is much harder than just asking to be forgiven, so we take the easier option, even if it doesn't help."
		<</if>>
	<<elseif $demon gte 6 and $transformationParts.demon.wings isnot "hidden">>
		<<His>> fingers run up and down your wings.
		<<if $gwylanTalked.includes("succubus")>>
			"You've presented your most precious vulnerabilities to me. You must really trust me." <<He>> giggles. "I appreciate it. There is a dark beauty to these wings. I understand why it can be so hard to let go, to endure that searing light in your head."
		<<else>>
			"There is a dark beauty to them. I understand why it can be so hard to let go, to endure that searing light in your head."
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<<He>> cups your cheek. "There are ways to be rid of it, but such things take time. I'll ensure you're at peace with it until that time comes."
	<</if>>
	/* ToDo: Gwylan - ghostbrew intro here? */

	<<if _gwylanTF.known and $fox gte 4>>
		<<He>> looks away, but you think you see the slightest hint of sadness on <<his>> face as <<he>> does.
	<</if>>
<<elseif $phase is "cow">>
	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>"It's too... dehumanising," you say. "I was treated like a real cow on that farm. I can't move on if I look like this."
		<<case "bratty">>"I hate it. I hate what that farm did to me. I hate feeling ashamed for wanting to act human."
		<<default>>"It brings backs memories of the farm. I can't stand it."
	<</switch>>
	<br><br>

	Gwylan nods solemnly.
<<elseif $phase is "purity">>
	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>"I can't ever be pure again, but... I at least want to go back to the way I was before," you say.
		<<case "bratty">>"I don't want to think about how I was before anymore," you say.
		<<default>>"It's nothing but a reminder of what things were like before," you say.
	<</switch>>
	<br><br>

	"You can't erase it," <<he>> says quickly. "There's no erasing it, ever. There's no forgetting either. There's only acceptance, or misery." <<He>> smiles. "Let's work on the former."
<<else>>
	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>"I... I'm in..." You can't muster the words.
		<<case "bratty">>"I'm bothered. Sexually. Like an animal."
		<<default>>"It's that time of year," you say, trying to hide your embarrassment.
	<</switch>>
	<br><br>

	<<if _gwylanTF.known>>
		<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("heat")>>
			<<He>> snickers. "That makes two of us. Maybe we should do something about that later."
		<<else>>
			<<He>> smiles. "I know something that can help relieve the pressure. I don't usually have to deal with it myself, I'm a bit... numb to it." <<He>> puts <<his>> hands over <<his>> belly.
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<<He>> smiles. "I understand. It's a hard impulse to overcome. This won't rid you of that, but it may at least make you feel less animalistic about it."
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if $hypnosis_potency gt 4 or $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 4>>
	<<He>> raises a single finger. "Follow it." <<He>> moves <<his>> hand side to side, then up and down. You follow it, and as you do, it almost looks like a small light forms on the tip.
	<br><br>

	<span class="purple">You quickly realise you're no longer able to look away.</span>
<<else>>
	<<He>> reaches into the neck of <<his>> robes, and pulls out a pendant tipped with <<if $gwylanTalked.includes("jasper")>>jasper<<else>>a reddish gem<</if>>. "Follow it." <<He>> moves it side to side. Your eyes follow.
<</if>>
<br><br>

"There's nothing in the forest except us." Everything outside the room slowly fades away. The corners of your vision blur, until there's nothing left but Gwylan.
"Good. The next time you doubt your inner self, remember..."
<br><br>

<<set $_devotionUp to 10 + $hypnosis_potency>>
<<gwylanHypnosis "devotion" $_devotionUp>>
<br><br>

<<He>> snaps <<his>> fingers, and you're no longer where you once were.
<br><br>

<<link [[Next|Gwylan Hypnosis Peace 2]]>><<pass 10>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Peace 2
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<gwylanHypnoCanvas>><<strip>>

<<revealTransformations>>

<<set _tf to checkTFparts()>>
<<set _earFind to Object.keys(T.tf).find(ear => ear.includes("Ears"))>>
<<switch _earFind>>
	<<case "wolfEars">><<set _earText to "wolf ears">>
	<<case "catEars">><<set _earText to "cat ears">>
	<<case "cowEars">><<set _earText to "cow ears">>
	<<case "foxEars">><<set _earText to "fox ears">>
	<<default>><<set _earText to "error">>
<</switch>>
<<set _tailFind to Object.keys(T.tf).find(tail => tail.includes("Tail") && tail !== "demonTail_colour")>>
<<switch _tailFind>>
	<<case "wolfTail">><<set _tailText to "wolf tail">>
	<<case "catTail">><<set _tailText to "cat tail">>
	<<case "cowTail">><<set _tailText to "cow tail">>
	<<case "foxTail">><<set _tailText to "fox tail">>
	<<case "birdTail">><<set _tailText to "bird tail">>
	<<case "demonTail">><<set _tailText to "demon tail">>
	<<default>><<set _tailText to "error">>
<</switch>>

You lie in a sea of roses. You feel more naked than you've ever been.
<<if _unhidden>>
	The parts of yourself that you were previously hiding are exposed.
<</if>>
Someone is watching you, unravelling you with their gaze, but you don't know from where.
<br><br>

<<if _tf.wolfEars or _tf.catEars or _tf.foxEars>>
	"Sharpest of ears, listen well."
<<elseif _tf.cowEars>>
	<<if $phase is "cow">>
		"Docile ears, seeking to return to humanity. Listen well."
	<<else>>
		"Docile ears, yearning for the praise of cattle. Listen well."
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	"Listen well."
<</if>>
The voice makes you jump as it reverberates around you. The roses all tremble in unison.
<span class="purple">You feel a breath on your ears.</span> You turn, and there's nobody. <<stress 2>><<gstress>>
<br><br>

The sky is pink. You feel fingers creep along your skin. A storm of rose petals swirls around you, and when they pass, Gwylan is embracing you.
<br><br>

<b>"<span class="witch">Delusion. Truth. The only difference is the face of the coin.</span>"</b>
<br><br>

<<if _earFind>>
	<<His>> hand runs along your head, rubbing your <<= _earText>>. <<He>> whispers. "Let them listen softly. The harsh sounds of civilisation are grating.
	Let there be no shame in hiding them away, lest your hearing become dull." <<He>> places <<his>> other hand on them, and lifts. <span class="red">Your ears lift away.</span>

	It looks like a headband.
	<<if _tf.cowHorns or _tf.demonHorns>>
		Your horns are on it, too.
	<</if>>
	<<He>> holds it in front of you, ensuring you can see it.
	<<if _tf.foxEars and _gwylanTF.known>>
		"I won't deny how this pains me, too. I see in you a kindred spirit, and it breaks my heart to see you made to hide away your beauty. I hope you'll still show your true self to me."
	<</if>>
	<<He>> puts it in your hands. "They will be here for you when you wish to hear the truth again."
	<br><br>
<<elseif _tf.cowHorns or _tf.demonHorns>>
	<<His>> hand runs along your head, rubbing your horns. <<He>> whispers. "Shave them down, if you wish. They will grow back in time, when you feel you need their protection again."
	<<He>> places <<his>> other hand on them, and lifts. <span class="red">Your horns lift away.</span>
	It looks like a headband. <<He>> holds it in front of you, ensuring you can see it. <<He>> puts it in your hands.
	<br><br>
<</if>>

<<if _tf.angelHalo>>
	You hear a soft, metallic thrum as <<he>> runs <<his>> hand along your halo. "The light can't remain forever. A candle must be snuffed to allow one to rest."
	<<He>> gently grasps it, <span class="red">and pulls.</span>
	It's a headpiece with translucent resin, giving it the appearance of a real floating halo. It reflects the light extremely well.
	"When the darkness becomes too much, one merely needs to light another. Keep it safe, and it will keep you safe in turn."
	<br><br>
<<elseif _tf.fallenAngelHalo>>
	You hear a discordant thrum as <<he>> runs <<his>> hand along the shards of your halo. "Are you ashamed? Is this self-flagellation for your loss?"
	<<He>> gently grasps it, <span class="red">and pulls.</span>
	It's a headpiece with translucent resin, giving it the appearance of a real floating halo. It's cracked and deformed in several places.
	"It's healthy to look back upon what could have been done differently, but it should not consume you. Life goes on, my dear."
	<br><br>
<</if>>

<<if _tailFind>>
	<<His>> hands trace down your body, making you shiver. They stop around your <<bottom>>. You suddenly feel off balance.
	<<He>> walks around you, <span class="red">now holding your disembodied <<= _tailText>></span>. There's an angled, rigid clip on the end.
	"Balance. Attracting mates. One must learn to crawl before they can walk, and you, my gentle one, face the challenge of sprinting in two different worlds."
	<<He>> hands you your tail. "The pace is yours to set. It will be ready for you to rejoin the wild, but only when you are, too."
	<br><br>
<</if>>

<<if _tf.catHeterochromia>>
	<<He>> cups your cheeks, and <<his>> hand approaches your eye. <span class="red"><<He>> pulls out a coloured contact lens.</span>
	"The eyes are the window to the soul. Does yours hold many facets?" <<He>> places it in a small case, and hands it to you.
	<br><br>
<</if>>

<<if _tf.birdWings or _tf.angelWings or _tf.fallenAngelWings or _tf.demonWings>>
	<<His>> arms wrap around you again. <<His>> hands rub your wings.
	<<if _tf.birdWings>>
		"These wings, these magnificent wings. If you find them too beautiful to show the world, let them fold without guilt. The sky will be waiting for you."
		You hear several clicks, and a sudden weight drops from your body. You somehow feel both lighter and heavier.
		<span class="red"><<He>> holds a strange backpack-like device, with large wing membranes on each side of it.</span> It's covered in straps and chords.
		"Only where the wind permits." Feathers fall all around you.
	<<elseif _tf.demonWings>>
		"An extra pair of limbs to embrace. Ever closer. A provocation themselves. Such things must be tempered."
		You hear a click, and a sudden weight drops from your body. You somehow feel both lighter and heavier.
		<span class="red"><<He>> holds a pair of bat-like wings.</span>
		"Should you need their comfort again, their embrace will return."
	<<else>>
		"Radiance. Tragedy. The most intimate reflections."
		You hear a click, and a sudden weight drops from your body. You somehow feel both lighter and heavier.
		<span class="red"><<He>> holds a pair of angel wings.</span>
		<<if _tf.fallenAngelWings>>
			They're worn and tattered.
		<<else>>
			They're white and fluffy.
		<</if>>
		"Should you need their comfort again, their embrace will return."
	<</if>>
	<br><br>
<</if>>

You feel like you've been shattered. You huddle in on yourself, scared and confused, clutching the pieces torn from your body. Was it ever real? <<trauma 16>><<ggtrauma>>
<br><br>

Just as you're about to slip further, <span class="green">they return to you</span>.
"Do you understand?" Gwylan holds you tightly, stroking your hair. "Justifications. Illusions. All that matters is what you believe, and what you can bear."
<<if _tf.birdWings or _tf.angelWings or _tf.fallenAngelWings or _tf.demonWings>>
	<<He>> rubs your wings. They can feel <<his>> hands.
<</if>>
<<if _tailFind>>
	Your tail moves on its own.
<</if>>
<<if _earFind>>
	You hear <<his>> whispers through your <<= _earText>>.
<</if>>
<<if _tf.angelHalo>>
	Your halo lights <<his>> face.
<<elseif _tf.fallenAngelHalo>>
	Your broken halo briefly comes back together.
<</if>>
<br><br>

With or without them, real or facsimile, you feel whole.
<br><br>

<<set _hypnoDays to 10 + ($hypnosis_potency * 3)>>
<<gwylanHypnosis "peace" _hypnoDays>>
<br><br>

<<if $fox gte 6 and $gwylanSeen.includes("romance") and $phase is "identity">>
	<<link [[Next|Gwylan Hypnosis Peace Fox Breakdown]]>><</link>>
<<else>>
	"Awaken." <<He>> snaps <<his>> fingers.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Next|Gwylan Hypnosis Peace Wake]]>><<pass 30>><<clotheson>><</link>>
<</if>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Peace Fox Breakdown
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
You close your eyes.
<br><br>

Nothing happens. You're still in the sea of roses.
<br><br>

Gwylan stares down at you. <span class="purple"><<His>> expression has changed.</span> <<His>> fox ears twitch.
<br><br>

"My dearest kin..." <<His>> mouth comes close to yours. "You're breaking my heart."
<br><br>

<span class="red">The sky turns a deep red.</span> "You say this isn't who you are?" <<His>> voice isn't gentle anymore.
"You are the only other person in the world who understands what this is like, to be mated for life. You promised forever. Now you tell me that it isn't who you are?"
<br><br>

<<His>> breathing is fast and shallow. <<His>> pupils are slits. "Do you wish to abandon what you are? Do you wish to leave me cold and alone again?"
<br><br>

<<He>> looks around in panic and confusion. <span class="purple">You only now realise that <<his>> lips aren't moving when <<he>> speaks anymore.</span>
<<He>> puts <<his>> hands over <<his>> ears.
<br><br>

"You're the only one who understands." A crack forms on <<his>> forehead.<br>
"Perhaps you don't understand enough." The crack escapes <<his>> head, taking the shape of an antler.<br>
"Perhaps you need to learn what an eternity alone feels like." The sky begins turning black.<br>
"Without me." Gwylan starts getting pulled away from you. <<He>> reaches out for you in desperation.<br>
"When it all returns to the tide."
<br><br>

You're both pulled into a black abyss. <<trauma 36>><<npcincr Gwylan dom -30>><<gggtrauma>><<lllyearning>>
<br><br>

"<<gwylanCommand "Awaken!">>" Gwylan desperately screams as <<his>> head is pulled under.
<br><br>

<<link [[...|Gwylan Hypnosis Peace Wake]]>><<pass 30>><<set $phase2 to "breakdown">><<clotheson>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Peace Wake
<<set $location to "forest_shop_garden">><<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<set _tf to checkTFparts()>>
<<canvas-model-override "clear">>
<<rehideTransformations>>

<<if $phase2 is "breakdown">>
	Your focus snaps back. You're back in the garden.
	<br><br>

	Gwylan is still holding you. <<His>> hands are shaking. "I'm sorry about that," <<he>> says unsteadily. "I... I suppose I had some bad thoughts of my own that needed to be put away."
	<<He>> looks up. Tears streak down <<his>> face, but <<he>> quickly wipes them away. "I'm fine."
<<else>>
	Your focus slowly returns. You're back in the garden.
	<<if $fox gte 6>>
		Gwylan is sitting behind you, brushing your tail. <<He>> pulls out clumps of loose fur, and it looks much more sleek than it did before.
		<br><br>

		<<if _gwylanTF.known>>
			"...and I personally find that pet shampoo works just as well, and leaves it quite fragrant.
			<<if random (0, 1) and !$gwylanSeen.includes("romance")>>
				If you've got a regular bed partner, you can use some perfumes made for people with allergies or sensitive skin.
				I recommend scents that can help soothe your partner if they have a habit of hugging your tail in their sleep, or spice things up when it's time to get hot and heavy, depending on what you want."
			<<else>>
				How do you think mine smells, dear?" <<His>> tail whiffs across your nose.
				<br><br>

				You rub your eyes. "It smells like fresh rain," you say.
				<br><br>

				<<He>> giggles. "So, like the rest of me, then."
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			"...and I personally find that pet shampoo works just as well, although I wouldn't recommend trying to get that close to a wild fox in most circumstances unless you really know what you're doing."
		<</if>>
		<<He>> spends some more time brushing it. It feels good.
		<<if !_tf.foxTail>>
			When <<he>> releases your tail, it vanishes the next time you blink.
		<</if>>
		<<stress -3>><<lstress>>
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

