<<set $location to "meadow">><<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<gwylanHypnoCanvas>><<set $slumberDifficultyLow to 300>><<set $slumberDifficultyHigh to 600>>
<<if $hypnosis_traits.slumber>>
	<<set $slumberDifficultyLow -= 100>><<set $slumberDifficultyHigh -= 100>>
<</if>>
Your eyes flutter open. <span class="red">You're inside a gargantuan rib cage.</span> The ribs are made of wood bleached white. A thin membrane stretches in between each massive trunk. It expands and contracts in a way that reminds you of breathing.
You find that you match the rhythm of its rise and fall.
<br><br>

A voice breaks your trance. "Can't sleep, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "name">>?"
<br><br>

You turn around. Gwylan sits in front of you amid a bed of <<if isLoveInterest("Gwylan")>>pink<<else>>red and white<</if>> roses. <<He>> twirls one by its stem.
<br><br>

"I can't either," <<he>> continues. "It's keeping me awake."
<br><br>

<<He>> points, but you don't need <<him>> to. You can hear the song coming from behind <<him>>. It's all you can hear. The call of something that has spent an eternity alone, only to find a kindred spirit at last.
<br><br>

<<if $nightmares gte 1>>
	<<link [[Confront your nightmares|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Nightmares]]>><</link>><<gtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>><<note "Nightmares" "blue">>
	<br>
<<else>>
	<<link [[Delve into a nightmare|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Nightmares]]>><</link>><<gggtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>><<willpowerdifficulty $slumberDifficultyLow $slumberDifficultyHigh>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<link [[Turn away and escape the vision|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Nightmares]]>><<set $phase to "wake">><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Nightmares
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $nightmares gte 1 and $phase isnot "wake">>
	<<set _continue to true>>
	<span class="blue">You're no stranger to nightmares.</span> <<trauma 12>><<set $hypnosis_potency++>><<gtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>>
<<elseif $willpowerSuccess and $phase isnot "wake">>
	<<set _continue to true>><<set $slumberDifficultyLow += 200>><<set $slumberDifficultyHigh += 200>>
	<span class="green">You shake away the tingling fear shooting through your fingertips.</span> They yearn to hold something. <<trauma 50>><<set $hypnosis_potency++>><<gggtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>>
<<else>>
	<<if $phase isnot "wake">>
		<span class="red">You stand paralysed.</span> The ribcage becomes still, as does your breathing. Gwylan stands, taking your hands.
		<br><br>
	<</if>>

	You turn away from the song, and focus on Gwylan. <<He>> smiles sadly. "Without confronting our nightmares, they will only fester into something darker."
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if _continue>>
	<<tiredness -1>><<pass 10>>
	You walk around Gwylan. <<He>> doesn't stop you. A knife rests buried in the ground just behind <<him>>. Its handle is made of bone. A circle of purple bulbs sway around it. They part for you as you advance.
	The knife's song grows louder. It is deep and mournful, pulling at parts of you that you didn't know existed.
	<br><br>

	"I can't," Gwylan says. "This isn't my thorn to pull."
	<br><br>

	<<Hes>> standing next to you now. <<His>> hand is around your wrist. Nails bite into your skin. A thin sheen of sweat glistens on <<his>> brow. <<His>> eyes are trained on the knife, pupils little more than dots in the middle of <<his>> irises.
	<br><br>

	"Please be careful," <<he>> says. "To yank it out carelessly will only leave you bloodied."
	<br><br>

	The knife's song grows louder. It bounces off the wooden ribs. Splinters fall to the ground, littering among the roses, as rot spreads from within.
	It wriggles out of the cracks with writhing shadows shaped like <<if $settings.tentaclesEnabled>>tentacles<<else>>hands<</if>>.
	<br><br>

	Red sea water weeps from the knife handle. The ribcage expands and contracts faster.
	<br><br>

	<<if $anxiety gte 1>>
		<<link [[Embrace your anxiety|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Anxiety]]>><</link>><<gtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>><<anxiety_disorder_text>>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		<<link [[Let yourself worry|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Anxiety]]>><</link>><<gggtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>><<willpowerdifficulty $slumberDifficultyLow $slumberDifficultyHigh>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<<link [[Let it fester|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Anxiety]]>><<set $phase to "wake">><</link>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	The emptiness fills.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Next|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Wake]]>><<pass 30>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Anxiety
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $anxiety gte 1 and $phase isnot "wake">>
	<<set _continue to true>>
	<span class="blue">You've been in darker places and seen what lies within.</span> You squeeze Gwylan's hand back.
<<elseif $willpowerSuccess and $phase isnot "wake">>
	<<set _continue to true>><<set $slumberDifficultyLow += 200>><<set $slumberDifficultyHigh += 200>>
	<span class="green">You squeeze Gwylan's hand back.</span>
<<else>>
	<<if $phase isnot "wake">>
		<span class="red">You can't resist. You need this thorn out of your paw.</span>
		<br><br>
	<</if>>

	You break free from Gwylan's grasp and take the knife by the handle, before yanking it out. Red seawater erupts from the wound, which grows with each pulse.
	Gwylan winces. "To bleed, or to fester. An impossible choice."
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if _continue>>
	<<tiredness -1>><<pass 10>>
	The knife calls to you. An urge to pick it up itches in your hand. You watch it move as if controlled by a string from far below. Gwylan clutches your wrist so hard you worry that <<he>>'ll break skin.
	<br><br>

	"Don't," <<he>> says. "You want to yank it out, but you have to be gentle. Slow."
	<br><br>

	You half-listen to <<him>>. It's begging you. After so long, It found you. You reach out, and wrap your hand around it.
	<br><br>

	The water reaches your ankles, but <span class="witch">you resist the call,</span> only lightly moving it. It hurts.
	<br>
	The water laps at your waist,
	<<if $willpower gte $slumberDifficultyLow>>
		<<set $slumberDifficultyLow += 50>><<set $slumberDifficultyHigh += 50>>
		but <span class="witch">you resist the call.</span> You slowly pull upwards. <<trauma 12>><<set $hypnosis_potency++>><<gtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>>
		<br>
		Your chest goes numb from the cold,
		<<if $willpower gte $slumberDifficultyLow>>
			<<set $slumberDifficultyLow += 75>><<set $slumberDifficultyHigh += 75>>
			but <span class="witch">you resist the call.</span> You exhale slowly as the red water flows faster. <<trauma 24>><<set $hypnosis_potency++>><<ggtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>>
			<br>
			You have to fight to keep your head above water,
			<<if $willpower gte $slumberDifficultyLow>>
				<<set _unbloodied to true>>
				<<set $slumberDifficultyLow += 100>><<set $slumberDifficultyHigh += 100>>
				but <span class="witch">you resist the call.</span> The knife is nearly free. <<trauma 50>><<set $hypnosis_potency++>><<gggtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>>
				<br>
				The waves close over your head,
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
	<<if _unbloodied>>
		and you finally succumb... but you're already holding the freed blade. You didn't feel a thing. The ground around you crumbles.
		<br><br>

		Gwylan smiles, and crumbles.
	<<else>>
		and you <span class="erase-from-history">succumb,</span> yank<span class="erase-from-history">ing</span> the blade free. It slides free from the ground with no resistance. As it does, the ground around it crumbles.
		<br><br>

		Gwylan crumbles.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	You crumble.
	<br><br>

	Nobody is left in the dark.
	<br><br>

	<<if $panicattacks gte 1>>
		<<link [[Clutch your panic|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Panic]]>><</link>><<gtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>><<note "Panic Attacks" "pink">>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		<<link [[Embrace the panic|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Panic]]>><</link>><<gggtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>><<willpowerdifficulty $slumberDifficultyLow $slumberDifficultyHigh>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<<link [[Shut out everything|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Panic]]>><<set $phase to "wake">><</link>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	The emptiness fills.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Next|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Wake]]>><<pass 30>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Panic
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $panicattacks gte 1 and $phase isnot "wake">>
	<<set _continue to true>>
	<span class="blue">You've been more afraid.</span> <<trauma 12>><<set $hypnosis_potency++>><<gtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>>
<<elseif $willpowerSuccess and $phase isnot "wake">>
	<<set _continue to true>><<set $slumberDifficultyLow += 200>><<set $slumberDifficultyHigh += 200>>
	<span class="green">You keep your eyes open,</span> although it's hard to tell. Everything is pitch black. <<trauma 50>><<set $hypnosis_potency++>><<gggtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>>
<<else>>
	<<if $phase isnot "wake">>
		<span class="red">You curl in on yourself.</span> You keep curling, your own body twisting and contorting... if only you had one.
		<br><br>
	<</if>>

	You lay still in emptiness, until something starts to break through the dark.
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if _continue>>
	<<canvas-model-override "arm_right" "hold">>
	<<wearProp "whale bone dagger">>
	<<tiredness -1>><<pass 10>>
	Only the knife lights your way. Its blue-white glow casts dark shadows that writhe and reach. You feel them caress you, trying to worm inside of you. Your muscles seize as you remember all of the suffering that has been inflicted upon you.
	<br><br>

	The shadows grow closer. One wraps <<if $settings.tentaclesEnabled>>a tentacle<<else>>its fingers<</if>> around your wrist. Another tries to pry your lips apart.
	<br><br>

	The knife begins to burn in your hand. You slash wildly. Bits of shadow fall to the ground and ooze back to the waiting void. You keep slashing, driven by an animalistic urge to be safe.
	<br><br>

	Except there is no safety in the dark. Not even the knife can protect you. The shadows, sensing triumph is close at hand, close over you. They promise you the bliss of Nothing.
	<br><br>

	<<if $flashbacks gte 1>>
		<<link [[Remember|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Flashbacks]]>><</link>><<gtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>><<note "Flashbacks" "purple">>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		<<link [[Attempt to stir your memory|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Flashbacks]]>><</link>><<gggtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>><<willpowerdifficulty $slumberDifficultyLow $slumberDifficultyHigh>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<<link [[Forget|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Flashbacks]]>><<set $phase to "wake">><</link>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	The emptiness fills.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Next|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Wake]]>><<pass 30>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Flashbacks
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $flashbacks gte 1 and $phase isnot "wake">>
	<<set _continue to true>>
	<span class="blue">You remember being through this.</span> <<trauma 12>><<set $hypnosis_potency++>><<gtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>>
<<elseif $willpowerSuccess and $phase isnot "wake">>
	<<set _continue to true>><<set $slumberDifficultyLow += 200>><<set $slumberDifficultyHigh += 200>>
	<span class="green">You remember who, and where, you are. You remember that this was all painfully real, once.</span> <<trauma 50>><<set $hypnosis_potency++>><<gggtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>>
<<else>>
	<span class="red">You forget the violation, but the emptiness remains. You forget the pain, but your skin still stings.</span> You tell yourself that you're better. A comforting lie.
	<br><br>

	You shut out the probing limbs, until something begins to appear in the darkness.
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if _continue>>
	<<tiredness -1>><<pass 10>>
	Shadows undulate all over your body. They reach in between your legs. Even more pry open your mouth and force their way inside. Grasping, squeezing hands. Fingers probing the most private parts of you.
	You writhe under all of the assaults you've ever faced.
	<br><br>

	It's too much. You sink lower into the dark.
	<br><br>

	There is nothing. There is nobody.
	<br><br>

	A voice whispers in your ear. "<span class="witch">Is this what you wanted?</span>"
	<br><br>

	You twitch.
	<br><br>

	"<span class="witch">Is this the life you want to live?</span>"
	<br><br>

	You inhale what feels like shards of frozen glass.
	<br><br>

	<<if $auriga_scar>>
		"<span class="witch">Rise, <<pcpetname "Gwylan">>. The void may promise comfort, but it is false, and the price is your soul.</span>"
	<<else>>
		"<span class="witch">Rise, <<pcpetname "Gwylan">>. To shut out the shadows is to give them power. The unknown and forgotten are always the more terrifying.</span>"
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	The knife burns. Its light becomes searing. The shadows retreat in waves of oily, oozing blackness. You are left on the floor naked and revealed.
	<<revealTransformations>>

	You stand on shaking legs. Ahead of you is darkness. Behind you is a wall of dirt. All above you is the rib cage. Once white wood has decayed to brittle black. Insects crawl in and out of holes, their shells like shining jewels.
	<br><br>

	There is a trail of <<if isLoveInterest("Gwylan")>>pink<<else>>alternating red and white<</if>> roses leading into the dark. A sweet voice sings to you from far away. You lift your knife and follow its sound.
	<br><br>

	<<if $dissociation gte 1>>
		<<link [[There's something wrong with you|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Visibly Disturbed]]>><</link>><<ggtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>><<note "and nobody can tell" "red">>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		<<link [[Brave the dark|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Visibly Disturbed]]>><</link>><<gggtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>><<willpowerdifficulty $slumberDifficultyLow $slumberDifficultyHigh>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<<link [[Wake up|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Visibly Disturbed]]>><<set $phase to "wake">><</link>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	The emptiness fills.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Next|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Wake]]>><<pass 30>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Visibly Disturbed
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $dissociation gte 1 and $phase isnot "wake">>
	<<set _continue to true>>
	<span class="blue">Nobody knows you. Nobody knows you better than anybody.</span> <<trauma 25>><<set $hypnosis_potency++>><<ggtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>>
<<elseif $willpowerSuccess and $phase isnot "wake">>
	<<set _continue to true>><<set $slumberDifficultyLow += 200>><<set $slumberDifficultyHigh += 200>>
	<span class="green">You grip the handle of the knife tighter, until it hurts. You're still here.</span> <<trauma 50>><<set $hypnosis_potency++>><<gggtrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>>
<<else>>
	<span class="red">You step the wrong way, and you fall.</span> Perhaps you did it on purpose. Perhaps you weren't ready to see what lays at the end, at your core.
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if _continue>>
	<<tiredness -1>><<pass 10>>
	<<canvas-model-override "arm_right" "idle">><<handheldon>>
	Each step brings a new change. Insects twist and warp. Some bulge. Slime oozes out between the chitin of their shells. Others grow bigger, or smaller. You think they're all staring at you.
	<br><br>

	The ribs change, too. Patches of bark crumble away to reveal water pierced by light. Somehow, the water does not fall onto you. You forge onwards. The roses guide you. The song buoys you. <span class="teal">It's familiar.</span>
	<br><br>

	It isn't until the song is so loud you can almost feel it that you realise you've been changing too. The scars inside of you have become real. <<if $rapestat + $moleststat gte 500>>Hand prints are burnt into your thighs.<</if>>
	Parts of you have disintegrated to reveal that same watery visage.
	<br><br>

	"It's beautiful, isn't it?"
	<br><br>

	You look up. Gwylan is sitting at the end of the trail of roses. <<He>> smiles at you. <<His>> mousy hair is long and flows all around <<him>> like a pool of water<<if _gwylanTF.known>>, resting on <<his>> tail<</if>>.
	<<if isLoveInterest("Gwylan")>>Pink<<else>>Red and white<</if>> roses adorn <<his>> body like a <<if $pronoun is "m">>robe<<else>>dress<</if>>. <<if _gwylanTF.known>><<His>> ears twitch.<</if>>
	<br><br>

	"We are always more beautiful when we reveal what's inside of us," <<he>> says. <<He>> holds up a tightly wound bundle of rose petals. "Like a chrysalis opening up to a butterfly."
	<br><br>

	<<He>> blows on the rose petals.
	<br><br>

	<<if $dissociation gte 2>>
		<<link [[This feels real|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Dissociation]]>><</link>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>><<note "Dissociation" "forest-green">>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		<<link [[This doesn't feel real|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Dissociation]]>><</link>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>><<willpowerdifficulty $slumberDifficultyLow $slumberDifficultyHigh>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<<link [[This isn't real|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Dissociation]]>><<set $phase to "wake">><</link>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	The emptiness fills.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Next|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Wake]]>><<pass 30>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Dissociation
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>

The petals scatter into the air. You watch as they flutter all around you in an explosion of colour. Roses bloom from the cracks in the wooden ribs. You see them bloom on your watery patches, too.
<br><br>

<<if $dissociation gte 1 and $phase isnot "wake">>
	<span class="forest-green">This feels real.</span> <<trauma -50>><<set $hypnosis_potency++>><<llltrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>>
<<elseif $willpowerSuccess and $phase isnot "wake">>
	<span class="green">You let them wash over you.</span> <<trauma -25>><<set $hypnosis_potency++>><<lltrauma>><<gwylanHypnoEffect>>
<<else>>
	<span class="red">You flinch away.</span> One brushes your cheek like a gentle caress, and you open your eyes again. You steady your breathing. The look on Gwylan's face makes you feel like everything will be alright.
<</if>>
<br><br>

Gwylan steps over to join you. "Embracing our struggles makes us human," <<he>> says. "Pain can be breathtaking in its cruel majesty. Every rose has its thorn."
<br><br>

Vines weave together to form a bed. Gwylan leads you to it and pulls you down. Despite the thorns poking into you, you find it comfortable. <<He>> strokes your hair. Warmth fills you.
<br><br>

"Sleep," <<he>> says. <<He>> pulls a blanket of roses over you both. "Sleep, <<pcpetname "Gwylan">>. Trauma is not something to run from. It's something to confront. To reflect upon. To remember." <<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><<gyearning>>
<br><br>

One of the rose petal butterflies lands on your hand. You smile and rest your head on Gwylan's chest. Soon, you are asleep, safe underneath the blanket of roses.
<br><br>

<<link [[Sleep|Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Wake]]>><<pass 30>><<set $phase to "end">><<tiredness -20>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Slumber Wake
<<set $location to "forest_shop_garden">><<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<canvas-model-override "clear">><<handheldon>>
<<unset $slumberDifficultyLow>><<unset $slumberDifficultyHigh>>
<<rehideTransformations>>
Your focus slowly returns. You're back in the garden.
<br><br>

The incense has burned out.
<<if $phase is "end">>
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("romance")>>
		Gwylan holds you tightly. <<Hes>> fallen asleep <<himself>>.
		<br><br>

		<<He>> pushes <<his>> head into your chest, and lets out a sigh of contentment. You idly stroke <<his>> hair. <<npcincr Gwylan dom 3>><<ggyearning>>
		<br><br>

		After some time, <<his>> eyes flutter open. <<He>> smiles at you. "Oh, silly me. I got too comfortable." <<He>> yawns. "I haven't slept that well in ages. I think you helped me just as much as I helped you."
	<<elseif _gwylanStatus.includesAny("aroused", "lust", "dom")>>
		Gwylan runs <<his>> fingers through your hair. "Sleep well? You were out for a while." <<He>> smiles. "You did well, going so deep into the trance."
	<<else>>
		Gwylan looks down at you, smiling. "Sleep well? You were out for a while." <<He>> giggles. "You did well, going so deep into the trance."
	<</if>>
	<<He>> helps you stand.
	<br><br>

	You feel rested. "You should find sleep coming to you easier now, and you won't spend as much time tossing and turning when the bad thoughts hit. In fact, you might find the bad thoughts make sleep come even easier."
<<else>>
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("romance")>>
		Gwylan still lays next to you, watching you. "Sleep well?"
	<<elseif _gwylanStatus.includesAny("aroused", "lust", "dom")>>
		Gwylan runs <<his>> fingers through your hair. "Sleep well?"
	<<else>>
		Gwylan looks down at you, smiling. "Sleep well?"
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<if $hypnosis_potency gte 6>>
		You feel rested. You nod at Gwylan, and <<he>> helps you stand.
		<br><br>

		"Wonderful! You should find sleep coming to you easier now, and you won't spend as much time tossing and turning when the bad thoughts hit. In fact, you might find the bad thoughts make sleep come even easier."
	<<else>>
		You feel a little more rested. You nod at Gwylan, and <<he>> helps you stand.
		<br><br>

		"You weren't asleep very long, <span class="blue">so the hypnosis might not last.</span> Regardless, you should find sleep coming to you easier now, and you won't spend as much time tossing and turning when the bad thoughts hit. In fact, you might find the bad thoughts make sleep come even easier."
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<<He>> starts to gather <<his>> things.
<br><br>

<<set _hypnoDays to 5 + Math.floor($hypnosis_potency * 1.5)>>
<<gwylanHypnosis "slumber" _hypnoDays>>
<br><br>

<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("hypnosis_slumber")>>

<<link [[Go back in the shop|Gwylan Hypnosis End]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Insight
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $phase is "tentacles">>
	<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("hypnosis_insight_tentacles")>>
	"I've seen monsters," you say. "Unnatural creatures with many grasping limbs, like tentacles."
	<br><br>

	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("likes_tentacles")>>
		Gwylan nods. "If you see them, they see you. If 'see' is the right word. You've done much more than seeing, from what you've told me."
	<<else>>
		Gwylan nods. "If you see them, they see you. If 'see' is the right word."
	<</if>>
<<elseif $phase is "plants">>
	<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("hypnosis_insight_plants")>>
	"I've seen plants come to life," you say. "I know they're already alive, but not like this. Not moving their branches, roots, and vines with malicious intent."
	<br><br>

	"There are songs I could teach you," Gwylan says. "But it would take a long time to learn them all, and it might not be enough."
<<elseif $phase is "slimes">>
	<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("hypnosis_insight_slimes")>>
	"I've seen blobs of slime, of different sizes," you say. "They move as if they have a will, and they're not friendly."
	<br><br>

	"I've seen them too," Gwylan says. "But their origin is a mystery to me. They used to be far more rare, but they've multiplied since the Violet Elk moved in. Perhaps they've agitated a nest underground while searching where they shouldn't. Or maybe they make them, deliberately or otherwise."
<<elseif $phase is "monsters">>
	<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("hypnosis_insight_monsters")>>
	"I've seen animals that appear to have human characteristics," you say. "Including speech. It's surreal, especially in the park when people are walking their dogs."
	<br><br>

	"Sounds fun," Gwylan says. "In moderation."
<<elseif $phase is "holes">>
	<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("hypnosis_insight_holes")>>
	"There are holes in reality," you say. "As the temple calls them. I see them sometimes, and the corruption seeping through."
	<br><br>

	Gwylan nods. "That's indeed what they call them. I—" <<he>> pauses, then seems to change <<his>> mind. "They can be distracting."
<<elseif $phase is "lots">>
	<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("hypnosis_insight_lots")>>
	"This might sound silly," you say. "But it's more than one thing. Shadows watching me. Eyes staring from impossible places. It's hard to look into the dark."
	<br><br>

	"Some threats only become dangerous if they're noticed," Gwylan says.
<</if>>
<br><br>

"It's not an easy thing, to forget what you know. It's too brutal, too costly. I can't offer you such. However," <<he>> decapitates a flower without looking at it, without needing to. "There's another way. An old way."
<br><br>

<<if $hypnosis_potency gt 4 or $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 4>>
	<<He>> raises a single finger. "Follow it." <<He>> moves <<his>> hand side to side, then up and down. You follow it, and as you do, it almost looks like a small light forms on the tip.
	<br><br>

	<span class="purple">You quickly realise you're no longer able to look away.</span>
<<else>>
	<<He>> reaches into the neck of <<his>> robes, and pulls out a pendant tipped with <<if $gwylanTalked.includes("jasper")>>jasper<<else>>a reddish gem<</if>>. "Follow it." <<He>> moves it side to side. Your eyes follow.
<</if>>
<br><br>

"There's nothing in the forest except us." Everything outside the room slowly fades away. The corners of your vision blur, until there's nothing left but Gwylan.
"Good. The next time you doubt your place in the world, remember..."
<br><br>

<<set $_devotionUp to 10 + $hypnosis_potency>>
<<gwylanHypnosis "devotion" $_devotionUp>>
<br><br>

<<He>> snaps <<his>> fingers, and you're no longer where you once were.
<br><br>
