:: Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Slimes
<<set $location to "underground">><<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<gwylanHypnoCanvas>>
You find yourself in a cave, lit by glowing crystals. They reverberate a little, releasing a gentle tinkling sound. The cave looks natural, but there are footprints leading into the dark.
<br><br>

You move your foot, and find a sticky substance clinging to your heel. You steady yourself against the wall, only to find the substance on your hand as well. Slime is oozing through cracks in the floor and walls, arising from somewhere unseen. You step away, and a dollop lands where you just stood. It's emerging from the ceiling.
<br><br>

Singing echoes through the cave. It almost sounds like the crystals are singing along, amplifying the sound. It promises security, yet that only agitates your anxiety. You walk towards the voice. The crystals become larger and more numerous, until you reach an open space full of them.
<br><br>

In the centre of the space sits a pool of water, reflecting the light from the crystal, and almost appearing to glow itself. You step to its shore, and see a pair of eyes staring up at you, a mischievous glimmer within. It's Gwylan. <<He>> gives you a reassuring smile, perhaps aware of how disconcerting <<he>> looks. Then <<he>> lifts a hand and presses it against the surface, as if <<he>> were trapped in one of the crystals, not floating in a pool.
<br><br>

<<link [[Reach for Gwylan|Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Slimes 2]]>><<set $phase2 to 1>><</link>>
<br>
<<link [[Step away|Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Slimes 2]]>><<set $phase2 to 2>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Slimes 2
<<effects>>
<<if $phase2 is 1>>
	You reach for Gwylan's hand, pushing it into the chill water. Gwylan takes your hand in <<hers>>. With an irresistible force, <<he>> pulls you into the water.
<<else>>
	You turn away, but the singing rings out, louder now, and with a new force to it. It sounds like an anxious parent, calling their child away from danger. The force proves irresistible. You turn back to the water.
	<br><br>

	Gwylan takes your hand in <<hers>>, and pulls you in.
<</if>>
<br><br>

A flash of green light disorients you as you enter, then you find yourself on your knees, on the ground beside the pool. Gwylan helps you to your feet. <<His>> clothes are dry.
<br><br>

"You're not actually wet, you know," Gwylan says, as if reading your mind. You look at the water, <span class="pink">and see a pair of eyes staring back.</span>
<br><br>

"Don't look at it." Gwylan takes both your hands. "Look at me. Remember this pool, and where I brought you. Now your inability to forget works in your favour, see?"
<br><br>

<<link [[Ask for more details on what's going on|Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Ask]]>><</link>>
<br>
<<link [[Nod|Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Nod]]>><</link>>
