:: Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Holes
<<set $location to "town">><<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<gwylanHypnoCanvas>>
You awaken in town, stood on what looks like High Street. Except it's all wrong. The buildings, cars, and trees all look fine in isolation, but together appear somehow alien from one another. It feels like the space between them is sick, swollen, about to burst open. Like your presence could cause an irreparable rupture. You dare not glance at the people.
<br><br>

You hear singing over the traffic. You follow the sound of the voice, careful not to look anyone in the eye, until you come to a tiered fountain. Water cascades from a platform, high above.
<br><br>

Other people are giving the fountain a wide berth. You peer into the falling water, and see a pair of eyes, bearing a mischievous glint. It's Gwylan. <<He>> gives you a reassuring smile, then reaches towards you. <<His>> hand presses against the waterfall, as if it were glass.
<br><br>

<<link [[Reach for Gwylan|Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Holes 2]]>><<set $phase2 to 1>><</link>>
<br>
<<link [[Step away|Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Holes 2]]>><<set $phase2 to 2>><</link>>
