<<if $phase2 is 1>>
	You reach through the water. Gwylan takes your hand, and pulls you in with an irresistible strength.
<<else>>
	You turn away from the fountain, <span class="red">only to find everyone on the street stood still, watching you.</span> You hear the singing again, now louder, and with the tone of an anxious parent calling their child away from danger.
	<br><br>

	The force proves irresistible. You turn back to the fountain and take Gwylan's hand. <<He>> pulls you in.
<</if>>
<br><br>

Your hands and knees find solid ground. You're kneeling in the fountain. Gwylan helps you to your feet, gives you a reassuring squeeze, and helps you step from the water. <<He>> looks dry, somehow.
<br><br>

"You're not actually wet, you know," Gwylan says as if reading your mind. You look back at the cascading water. <span class="pink">Another pair of eyes stare back.</span>
<br><br>

"Don't look at it." Gwylan takes both your hands. "Look at me. Remember this fountain, and where I brought you. Now your inability to forget works in your favour, see?"
<br><br>

<<link [[Ask for more details on what's going on|Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Ask]]>><</link>>
