:: Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Lots
<<set $location to "park">><<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<gwylanHypnoCanvas>>
You awaken in town, in what looks like the park. You feel an odd stillness. You hear none of the usual sounds of town.
<br><br>

An electricity crawls over the side of your neck, and your hair stands on end. Something is watching you. You turn to face the culprit, but see only trees and other plants. You feel the sensation again, this time on the back of your neck. You whirl, but still see nothing. You feel, more than hear, a mocking laughter, coming from the trees themselves. Or something within them.
<br><br>

The silence is broken by a sweet voice, singing. You follow the sound, until you come to a bridge over a river. Peering into the water, you see a pair of eyes staring back, bearing a mischievous glint. It's Gwylan. <<He>> gives you a reassuring smile, then reaches towards you. <<His>> fingers press against the river's surface, as if it were glass.
<br><br>

<<link [[Take Gwylan's hand|Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Lots 2]]>><<set $phase2 to 1>><</link>>
<br>
<<link [[Step away from the water|Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Lots 2]]>><<set $phase2 to 2>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Lots 2
<<effects>>

<<if $phase2 is 1>>
	You crouch, and reach through the side of the bridge. Gwylan grasps your hand. An irresistible force blows the bridge apart, and you fall into the water.
<<else>>
	You turn away, but hear the singing again. It's louder now, and carries an urgent tone, like an anxious parent calling their child away from danger. It proves an irresistible force. You turn back to Gwylan, and take <<his>> hand. The bridge collapses, and you fall into the water.
<</if>>
<br><br>

A flash of green light disorients you further, then you find yourself on your hands and knees on the riverbank. Gwylan crouches beside you, and helps you to your feet. <<He>> looks dry.
<br><br>

"You're not actually wet, you know," Gwylan says as if reading your mind. You look back at the rushing river. <span class="pink">Another pair of eyes stare back.</span>
<br><br>

"Don't look at it." Gwylan takes both your hands. "Look at me. Remember this river, and where I brought you. Now your inability to forget works in your favour, see?"
<br><br>

<<link [[Ask for more details on what's going on|Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Ask]]>><</link>>
<br>
<<link [[Nod|Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Nod]]>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Ask
<<effects>>
<<if $speech_attitude is "meek">>
	"I hope it's not impudent," you say. "But can you share some details on how this works?"
<<elseif $speech_attitude is "bratty">>
	"What was that thing in the water?" you ask. "It'll be easier to remember if you tell me what's going on."
<<else>>
	"What's watching me from the water?" you ask. "What did you do?"
<</if>>
<br><br>

"I just changed your perspective," Gwylan says. "I'd say I put you upside-down, but that implies there's a right way up. I dragged you into the water, don't look, and I dragged you from the water, but not both. Your compass now points south." <<He>> pauses. "Are these metaphors helping, or am I just confusing things further?"
<br><br>

<<He>> looks at the water, in thought. "You needn't worry about what you saw in there. Not unless you forget. That's the important thing." <<He>> snaps <<his>> fingers. "Awaken."
<br><br>

<<link [[Next|Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Wake]]>><<pass 30>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Nod
<<effects>>

You nod. Gwylan looks at the water, in thought. "You needn't worry about what you saw in there. Not unless you forget." <<He>> snaps <<his>> fingers. "Awaken."
<br><br>

<<link [[Next|Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Wake]]>><<pass 30>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Insight Wake
<<set $location to "forest_shop_garden">><<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<canvas-model-override "clear">>

Your focus slowly returns. You're back in the garden.
<br><br>

The incense has burned out. "Be aware. Perspectives can change." <<He>> starts to gather <<his>> things.
<br><br>

<<set _hypnoDays to 10 + ($hypnosis_potency * 2)>>
<<gwylanHypnosis "insight" _hypnoDays>>
<br><br>

<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("hypnosis_insight")>>

<<link [[Go back in the shop|Gwylan Hypnosis End]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Removal
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $phase is "suggestion">>
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("hypnosis_removal_suggestion")>>
		"I think Harper put ideas in my head again," you say.
		<br><br>

		Gwylan frowns. "I'll have to dig around in your head some more, then."
	<<else>>
		<<switch $speech_attitude>>
			<<case "meek">>"Th-there's this doctor, named Harper. <<nnpc_Hes "Harper">> been giving me treatments, but they don't feel right."
			<<case "bratty">>"There's this quack named Harper. <<nnpc_Hes "Harper">> been giving me treatments, but they're... not right."
			<<default>>"There's this doctor named Harper. <<nnpc_He "Harper">> keeps giving me these strange treatments, and they feel wrong, somehow."
		<</switch>>
		You think for a moment. "I can't remember why, though."
		<br><br>

		Gwylan's face sours. "I can imagine what you mean. I'll have to dig around in your head a little."
		<<if !$brownFoxRevealed>>
			<br><br>
			"Do you know <<nnpc_him "Harper">>?" you ask. <<He>> doesn't answer. Maybe <<he>> didn't hear you.
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
	<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("hypnosis_removal_suggestion")>>
<<elseif $phase is "scream">>
	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>"Whenever I... feel helpless, and like I want to scream for help, I end up hurting all over."
		<<case "bratty">>"There are times when I feel like I need to yell for someone to help me. Every time I do, I end up with bruises."
		<<default>>"Whenever I feel like I need to scream for help, I end up with bruises all over."
	<</switch>>
	<br><br>

	Gwylan nods. "I've heard this before. This should be easy to fix."
	<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("hypnosis_removal_scream")>>
<<elseif $phase is "cover">>
	"Whenever I get exposed and want to cover myself up, I just end up feeling even more exposed," you say.
	<br><br>

	Gwylan nods. "A common trick. We'll fix this."
	<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("hypnosis_removal_cover")>>
<<elseif $phase is "deviancy">>
	"Whenever I get attacked by animals, I think I end up provoking them somehow," you say.
	<br><br>

	<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 3>>
		Gwylan covers <<his>> mouth. "Oh dear. I hope that's not a side effect of what we've done together."
	<<else>>
		Gwylan frowns. "I'm familiar with such techniques. We'll fix this."
	<</if>>
	<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("hypnosis_removal_deviancy")>>
<<else>>
	"I can't remember. There's a lot of memories missing."
	<br><br>

	Gwylan nods. "I know how to bring up blocked memories. Let's have a dig through."
	<<set _hypnosisTypes to ["suggestion", "scream", "cover", "deviancy"].filter(h => V.hypnosis_traits[h] && V.hypnosis_traits[h] >= 1)>>
	<<if _hypnosisTypes.length>>
		<<set $phase to _hypnosisTypes.random()>>
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if $hypnosis_potency gt 4 or $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 4>>
	<<He>> raises a single finger. "Follow it." <<He>> moves <<his>> hand side to side, then up and down. You follow it, and as you do, it almost looks like a small light forms on the tip.
	<br><br>

	<span class="purple">You quickly realise you're no longer able to look away.</span>
<<else>>
	<<He>> reaches into the neck of <<his>> robes, and pulls out a pendant tipped with <<if $gwylanTalked.includes("jasper")>>jasper<<else>>a reddish gem<</if>>. "Follow it." <<He>> moves it side to side. Your eyes follow.
<</if>>
<br><br>

"There's nothing in the forest except us." Everything outside the room slowly fades away. The corners of your vision blur, until there's nothing left but Gwylan.
"Good. Tell me, when's the last time..."
<br><br>

<<set $_devotionUp to 10 + $hypnosis_potency>>
<<gwylanHypnosis "devotion" $_devotionUp>>
<br><br>

<<He>> snaps <<his>> fingers, and you're no longer where you once were.
<br><br>

<<switch $phase>>
	<<case "suggestion">><<link [[Next|Gwylan Hypnosis Removal Suggestion]]>><<pass 10>><</link>><br>
	<<case "scream">><<link [[Next|Gwylan Hypnosis Removal Scream]]>><<pass 10>><</link>><br>
	<<case "cover">><<link [[Next|Gwylan Hypnosis Removal Cover]]>><<pass 10>><</link>><br>
