:: Gwylan Hypnosis Removal Suggestion
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<gwylanHypnoCanvas>>
/* ToDo: Gwylan - underwhelming compared to others. Redo? */
The flash of a camera.
<br><br>

You feel dizzy as your eyes adjust.
<br><br>

<i>"...you won't remember this."</i> Harper's voice echoes in a white void.
