		<<He>> locks eyes with you. "Why?" Your head pounds painfully. <<pain 2>><<gpain>>
	<<else>> /* You want the hypnosis for its effects */
		<<switch $speech_attitude>>
			<<case "meek">>
				"It's just... the only way," you say quietly. "The only way to
			<<case "bratty">>
				"Because I don't have any other options," you say firmly. "It's the only way to
			<<default>>
				"It's the only way," you say, shrugging. "The only way to
		<</switch>>

		<<switch $phase>>
			<<case "peace">>
				come to peace with what I am."
			<<case "silence">>
				get rid of the <<pluralise numberOfEarSlime(true) "thing">> in my <<pluralise numberOfEarSlime(true) "ear">>."
			<<case "slumber">>
				have a good night's sleep."
			<<case "insight">>
				know what's real and what's not."
			<<case "removal">>
				have control of myself."
				<br><br>

				Gwylan laughs bitterly. "<<pcPetname "Gwylan" "simple">>, if you're worried about <i>control</i>, this is the last thing you should be doing."
		<</switch>>
		<br><br>

		<<if $phase isnot "removal">>
			Gwylan closes <<his>> eyes, frowning. "Not good enough, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "simple">>. This, what I'm about to do to you... it's not an acceptable byproduct for <i>anything</i>."
			<br><br>
		<</if>>

		<<switch $phase>>
			<<case "peace">>
				"But these pieces of myself—"
			<<case "silence">>
				"But the <<pluralise numberOfEarSlime(true) "slime">>—"
			<<case "slumber">>
				"But my sleep—"
			<<case "insight">>
				"But the visions—"
			<<case "removal">>
				"But the voices—"
		<</switch>>
		<br><br>

		"—<<= $phase is "slumber" or $phase is "silence" and numberOfEarSlime(true) is 1 ? "is" : "are">> not bad enough to justify this," <<he>> insists. "This is a cost too great for you to pay, unless you're certain you can accept it. Not just that; unless you're certain you want it."
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Say nothing|Gwylan Hypnosis Deepest]]>><<set $phase2 to 1>><<npcincr Gwylan dom -5>><</link>><<llyearning>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Say it makes you feel safe|Gwylan Hypnosis Deepest]]>><<set $phase2 to 4>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Say you like feeling closer to <<him>>|Gwylan Hypnosis Deepest]]>><<set $phase2 to 5>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><</link>><<gyearning>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Say you want answers|Gwylan Hypnosis Deepest]]>><<set $phase2 to 6>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<if $phase2 isnot 3>>
		<<link [[Say you just want the help you asked for|Gwylan Hypnosis Deepest]]>><<set $phase2 to 3>><<npcincr Gwylan dom -1>><</link>><<lyearning>>
	<</if>>
<<elseif $phase2 is 4 or $phase2 is 5 or $phase2 is 6>>
	<<if $phase2 is 4>> /* It makes you feel safe */
		You cross your arms over your chest.
		<<switch $speech_attitude>>
			<<case "meek">>
				"It... it makes me feel safe," you say. "You make me feel safe."
			<<case "bratty">>
				"The world is fucking scary," you say. "But what you do to me makes it feel safer."
			<<default>>
				"It makes me feel safe," you say. "Like you'll protect me from everything."
		<</switch>>
		<br><br>

		<<He>> looks at you sadly. "I'm not convinced."
	<<elseif $phase2 is 5>> /* You like feeling closer */
		You shuffle a little closer to <<him>>.
		<<switch $speech_attitude>>
			<<case "meek">>
				"I... I like how close it makes me feel to you," you say.
			<<case "bratty">>
				"I want to feel closer to you," you say. "Willingly."
			<<default>>
				"I like feeling this close to you," you say. "I want more."
		<</switch>>
		<br><br>

		<<His>> face reddens, but <<his>> expression doesn't change. "I'm not convinced."
	<<else>> /* You want answers */
		You look away. "There's something further down," you say. "I can't explain it, but I need to see it. I need the answer to this question."
		<br><br>

		<<He>> crosses <<his>> arms. "I'm not convinced."
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	Your vision gets blurry for a moment. You find some of your memories missing or out of order. <<trauma 6>><<gtrauma>>
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Stop|Gwylan Hypnosis Deepest]]>><<set $phase2 to 1>><<npcincr Gwylan dom -5>><</link>><<llyearning>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Beg|Gwylan Hypnosis Deepest]]>><<set $phase2 to 7>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<if hasSexStat("deviancy", 3)>>
		<<link [[Beg like a dog|Gwylan Hypnosis Deepest]]>><<set $phase2 to 8>><<npcincr Gwylan lust 5>><</link>><<deviant3>><<gglust>>
	<<else>>
		<<insufficientStat "deviancy" "to willingly beg like a dog">>
	<</if>>
	<br>
<<elseif $phase2 is 7 or $phase2 is 8>>
	<<set _tf to checkTFparts()>>
	<<if $phase2 is 7>> /* Beg */
		You bow your head. "Please," you say. "I want this. I really do."
		<br><br>

		"What was that? I didn't hear you." <<He>> crouches down to your eye level.
		<br><br>

		<<switch $speech_attitude>>
			<<case "meek">>
				"P-please!" you say louder.
			<<case "bratty">>
				You sigh and roll your eyes. "Pleeeeeease," you say.
			<<default>>
				"Please," you say louder.
		<</switch>>
		<br><br>

		"Please what?" <<He>> cups your cheek. "Tell me you want to do everything I say without question."
	<<else>> /* Bark like a dog */
		<<if $speech_attitude is "meek">>
			You straighten up on your knees,
		<<else>>
			You shift around to get on your knees,
		<</if>>
		folding your arms up to your chest.
		<<if _tf.wolfTail or _tf.catTail or _tf.cowTail or _tf.birdTail or _tf.foxTail or _tf.demonTail>>
			Your tail wags behind you.
		<</if>>
		<<if $worn.neck.collared is 1>>
			You <<pull_leash "give">> a tug for emphasis.
		<</if>>
		<<deviancy3>>

		<<if $worn.neck.collared is 1 and $worn.neck.type.includes("leash")>>
			<<He>> crouches down to your eye level, grabbing your leash and patting your head.
		<<else>>
			<<He>> crouches down to your eye level and pats your head.
		<</if>>
		"<<pcPetname "Gwylan" "good">>." <<arousal 500>><<garousal>>
		<br><br>

		<<He>> cups your cheek. "Tell me you want to do everything I say without question."
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<span class="purple">You feel the effects of the red powder wearing off. A heat rises within you, yearning for <<him>>.</span>
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Stay silent|Gwylan Hypnosis Deepest]]>><<set $phase2 to 1>><<npcincr Gwylan dom -5>><</link>><<llyearning>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Give <<him>> control|Gwylan Hypnosis Deepest Slip]]>><<set $phase2 to 0>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 3>><</link>><<ggyearning>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	<<set _hideHypnosisOptions to true>><<set $weekly.gwylanDeepest to true>>
	You let out a deep breath, but do nothing more.
	<br><br>

	Gwylan frowns. "Forgive me. I should have never let you sink this far."
	<br><br>

	<<set $phase to 0>><<set $phase2 to 0>>
	<<gwylanOptions>>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Deepest Slip
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("hypnosis_deepest")>>
<<set $phase2 to 0>>
<<if $hypnosisTimers.devotion>>
	<<set $hypnosisTimers.devotion.time to Math.clamp($hypnosisTimers.devotion.time, 75, 95)>>
<</if>>
You muster your willpower to make sure it sounds like you mean it.
<<switch $speech_attitude>>
	<<case "meek">>
		"I w-want... I want to do everything you say."
	<<case "bratty">>
		"I want to do everything you say. Without question."
	<<default>>
		"I want to... do everything you say... without question."
<</switch>>
<br><br>

"Tell me you want to belong to me," Gwylan says through ragged breaths. The shop begins to swirl around you in a haze.
<br><br>

"I want to belong to you," you say.
<br><br>

"Tell me you want to sink even deeper," <<he>> says, leaning towards you.
<br><br>

"I want to reach the bottom," you say, getting closer in turn.
<br><br>

"I suppose I have to believe you now, despite my doubts," <<he>> says, leaning away as you continually get even closer. "Dear, that's enough. Stop that." <<He>> pushes your face away gently.
<br><br>

Your lips itch. You feel your will is still your own for a precious few seconds, <span class="pink">yet part of you wants to slip even deeper,</span> as though you need to further prove yourself to <<him>>. Gwylan starts to stand. "Let's go."
<br><br>

<<link [[Follow <<him>>|Gwylan Hypnosis Start 2]]>><<endevent phaseless>><</link>>
<br>
<<link [[Tell Gwylan you love <<him>>|Gwylan Hypnosis Love]]>><<pass 1>><</link>><<gwylanHypnoNote "kiss">>
<br>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Love
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
"I love you," you say. "Those are my own words. Are they proof enough?"
<br><br>

<<His>> face goes beetroot-red. "That's just the hypnosis talking. It's not—"
<br><br>

You lean forward and close the minuscule remaining distance, kissing <<him>>.
<<His>> eyes widen and <<he>> lets out a tiny squeak. But <<he>> doesn't push you away. <<gwylanKiss>>
<br><br>

<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>>
	<<He>> gingerly returns it. <<His>> eyes close.
<<else>>
	<span class="green"><<He>> cautiously returns it. <<His>> eyes close.</span>
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<He>> pulls away after a moment, and flicks you on the nose. "You're too much," <<he>> huffs. <<npcincr Gwylan dom 5>><<ggyearning>>
<br><br>

<<He>> brushes <<himself>> off and stands, helping you to your feet too.
<br><br>

<<link [[Follow <<him>>|Gwylan Hypnosis Start 2]]>><<endevent phaseless>><</link>>
<br>
<<link [[Ask <<him>> to say it back|Gwylan Hypnosis Deepest Love 2]]>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Hypnosis Deepest Love 2
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<switch $speech_attitude>>
	<<case "meek">>
		"You're so insensitive! Say it back!" you pout.
	<<case "bratty">>
		You clear your throat. <<He>> looks back at you.
		<br><br>

		"Well?" you say.
		<br><br>

		"Out the front door and to the left, mind the winch, it's a bit rusty," <<he>> responds.
		<br><br>

		"Say it back, smartass."
	<<default>>
		"How rude," you say. "Say it back."
<</switch>>
<br><br>

<<He>> frowns, and turns away. "I've lied to you enough already." <<trauma 12>><<ggtrauma>>
<br><br>

<<link [[Follow <<him>>|Gwylan Hypnosis Start 2]]>><<endevent phaseless>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Talk Ear Slime
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("ear_slime")>>
<<if $gwylanJordanSlime>>
	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>
			"S-someone told me you can help with something in my <<pluralise numberOfEarSlime(true) "ear">>," you say.
		<<case "bratty">>
			"I heard that you can stop <<if numberOfEarSlime(true) gte 2>>these demons<<else>>this demon<</if>> in my ear from whispering sweet nothings," you say.
		<<default>>
			"Jordan said you can help me with <<if numberOfEarSlime(true) gte 2>>these things that are<<else>>this thing that's<</if>> whispering in my ear," you say.
	<</switch>>
<<else>>
	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>
			"S-so, you said you can help with my intrusive thoughts?"
		<<case "bratty">>
			"Please tell me you actually know how to get <<if numberOfEarSlime(true) gte 2>>these things out of my ears<<else>>this thing out of my ear<</if>>."
		<<default>>
			"You said you could help me with <<if numberOfEarSlime(true) gte 2>>these things in my ears<<else>>this thing in my ear<</if>>."
	<</switch>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<He>> nods, rummaging around in a shoebox. <<He>> pulls out a small metal object. <<He>> then walks around you,
<<if $bodysize is 3>>
	standing on the tips of <<his>> toes to look
<<elseif $bodysize is 0>>
	bending over to look
<<else>>
	tilting your head to look
<</if>>
into your ear. You feel the cool touch of metal on the lobe.
<<if numberOfEarSlime(true) gte 2>>
	<<He>> then walks around you, looking in your other ear, too.
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<He>> sighs. "You're host to
<<if numberOfEarSlime(true) gte 2>>
	a pair of terrible parasitic creatures. Ones that are capable of forcing you to protect them, overwriting your needs with their desires." <<He>> steps in front of you. "I don't have the tools to extract them safely, not anymore. I haven't needed such things in many years."
<<else>>
	a terrible parasitic creature. One that's capable of forcing you to protect it, overwriting your needs with its desires." <<He>> steps in front of you. "I don't have the tools to extract it safely, not anymore. I haven't needed such things in many years."
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<He>> turns <<his>> head and holds <<his>> earlobe forward. <span class="blue">There's a tiny tattoo shaped like an ornate X behind it.</span> The details are intricate, and some of the lines almost seem to be moving when you look too long.
It's far more advanced than anything you've seen from the local tattoo parlour.
<br><br>

"It's a bit late for that to be a good solution for you, and I'm low on stock to make the ink anyways. The only permanent solution is quite dangerous, and involves laying upon the sunken altar in Lake Whiteflower when the moon rises red.
Not only will you have to hold your breath for a very long time, <span class="red">but there's something in that lake that doesn't much appreciate trespassers</span>, and it's attracted to the presence of these very parasites."
<br><br>

<<He>> puts <<his>> hand to <<his>> chin. "I can help in the short term, at least. <span class="blue">I know a particular hypnosis technique that can silence <<if numberOfEarSlime(true) gte 2>>them<<else>>it<</if>>,</span> or at least let you automatically filter out <<if numberOfEarSlime(true) gte 2>>their<<else>>its<</if>> noises and chemical releases."
<br><br>

<<gwylanOptions>>

