	It's far more advanced than anything you've seen from the local tattoo parlour.
	<br><br>

	"It's a bit late for that to be a good solution for you, and I'm low on stock to make the ink anyways. The only permanent solution is quite dangerous, and involves laying upon the sunken altar in Lake Whiteflower when the moon rises red.
	Not only will you have to hold your breath for a very long time, <span class="red">but there's something in that lake that doesn't much appreciate trespassers</span>, and it's attracted to the presence of these very parasites."
